1.22.name: wordpress/application-maker-crm-edition
1.22.description:
BLUE ORIGAMI CRM FREE VERSION (Formerly Application Maker | CRM Edition) - A product from 15 Green leaves

Version: 1.4.1 | CRM | Last update date: 25th JULY 2013. And more releases to come soon.

Last update 27th JULY 2013: MAJOR UPDATE, V1.4.1 is the now BLUE ORIGAMI CRM FREE EDITION, with a lot of updates all along the system. And this is the FREE version of the pluign that will now have a PRO paying (cheap) VERSION.

Last update 1th June 2013: fully new DATAGRID fully in advanced Javascript and Ajax with a new and better data management and a new UI

Last update 4th june 2013: Fix a bug on new top nav + just updated missing files.... Sorry for the missing files in last commit...

Last update 3rd june 2013: IMPORTANT: Added a new topbar on Datagrid and Edit form pages. Reviewed a little bit the Datagrids.

Last update 1st june 2013: IMPORTANT the main page of each App has been rebuilt fully, for example the main page f
